.TH AADK-CLI 1 "April 2026" "AADK" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
aadk-cli \- command line client for AADK services
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B aadk-cli
\fICOMMAND\fR
[\fIARGS\fR...]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B aadk-cli
provides command line access to the AADK job, workflow, project, toolchain,
target, observe, and build services.
.PP
Run
.B aadk-cli --help
or
.B aadk-cli \fICOMMAND\fR --help
to inspect the available subcommands and arguments.
.SH FILES
.TP
.I ~/.local/share/aadk/state/cli-config.json
Persisted CLI configuration.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR aadk (1),
.BR aadk-ui (1)
